story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0200_10: Having a bit of trouble, Mr. Hero of Unova?
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0400_10: Hello there! Let us assist you.
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0500_10: You’re gonna get in our way, too?
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0600_10:
Well, yes. I can’t leave the future of Pasio in the
hands of people like you.
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0800_10:
Your ugliness is interfering with the chosen ones
who will decide the future of this world.
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_0900_10: The flames of my conviction won’t tolerate it!
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_1000_10:
So this...is the formula brought about by the island
of Pasio...?
story_final_02_06000/2401_1201_1100_10:
Nothing seems to be going according to
my calculations.
